# to [[correct]]; to [[rectify]]; to [[straighten out]]
#: {{zh-x|矯正|to correct}}
#: {{zh-x|矯枉過正|to overcorrect}}
#* {{zh-x|今 天下 鍛-甲 摩-劍，矯-箭 控-弦，轉-輸 軍糧，未 見 休 時，此 天下 所 共 憂 也。|Now, everyone is busy forging armours, sharpening swords, '''straightening''' arrows, drawing bowstrings, or transporting military provisions. Nobody has had any rest, and everyone is troubled by this.|ref=Hanshu}}
